### 7. CHAT TOOLS COMPOSITION

**Files:**
- Creator: `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain/richmond/app/src/server/chat/tools/index.ts`
- Types: `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain/richmond/app/src/server/chat/tools/types.ts`
